wait(1) local Player = game:GetService("Players").LocalPlayer local Character = Player.Character local Backpack = Player.Backpack
local Torso = Character:WaitForChild("Torso") local Head = Character:WaitForChild("Head") local RightShoulder = Torso:WaitForChild("Right Shoulder") local LeftShoulder = Torso:WaitForChild("Left Shoulder")
local Camera = workspace.CurrentCamera
local TweenService = game:GetService("TweenService") local TI = TweenInfo.new( 0.25, Enum.EasingStyle.Sine )
local TargetParts = { "Right Arm", "Left Arm" }
for _,Part in pairs(Character:GetChildren()) do if table.find(TargetParts, Part.Name) and Part:IsA("BasePart") then print(Part.Name) Part.LocalTransparencyModifier = Part.Transparency
Part:GetPropertyChangedSignal("LocalTransparencyModifier"):Connect(function() Part.LocalTransparencyModifier = Part.Transparency end) end end
while wait() do if Head.LocalTransparencyModifier > 0.7 then TweenService:Create(RightShoulder,TI,{C0=(Camera.CFrame * CFrame.new(1,-1,-0.7)):ToObjectSpace(Torso.CFrame):Inverse() * CFrame.Angles(0, math.pi/2, 0)}):Play() TweenService:Create(LeftShoulder,TI,{C0=(Camera.CFrame * CFrame.new(-1,-1,-0.7)):ToObjectSpace(Torso.CFrame):Inverse() * CFrame.Angles(0, -math.pi/2, 0)}):Play() else TweenService:Create(RightShoulder,TI,{C0=(CFrame.new(1,0.5,0) * CFrame.Angles(0,math.pi/2,0))}):Play() TweenService:Create(LeftShoulder,TI,{C0=(CFrame.new(-1,0.5,0) * CFrame.Angles(0,-math.pi/2,0))}):Play() end end
